import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import './Products.css'; function Products() { return (
{/* Hero Section */}

Our Products & Packages

Discover our comprehensive range of water sports lessons and training programs designed to help you master the art of kitesurfing, hydrofoiling, and wing foiling.

{/* Kitesurfing Packages */}

Kitesurfing Lessons

Beginner Package

Perfect for those new to kitesurfing. Learn the fundamentals of kite control, safety procedures, and basic riding techniques.

  • 3 x 2-hour lessons
  • All equipment provided
  • Safety briefing included
  • Insurance coverage
$299 Book Now

Intermediate Package

For those with basic kitesurfing experience. Master advanced techniques, jumps, and wave riding.

  • 5 x 2-hour lessons
  • Advanced techniques
  • Wave riding instruction
  • Video analysis
$499 Book Now

Advanced Package

For experienced riders looking to perfect their skills and learn advanced maneuvers.

  • 8 x 2-hour lessons
  • Advanced tricks & jumps
  • Competition preparation
  • Personalized coaching
$799 Book Now
{/* Hydrofoil Packages */}

Hydrofoil Lessons

Hydrofoil Basics

Learn the fundamentals of hydrofoiling with our expert instructors. Master balance and control on the foil.

  • 4 x 1.5-hour lessons
  • Foil equipment provided
  • Safety training
  • Progress tracking
$399 Book Now

Advanced Hydrofoil

Perfect your hydrofoil skills with advanced techniques and wave riding instruction.

  • 6 x 1.5-hour lessons
  • Advanced foil techniques
  • Wave riding skills
  • Performance analysis
$599 Book Now
{/* Wing Foil Packages */}

Wing Foil Lessons

Wing Foil Introduction

Discover the exciting world of wing foiling with our comprehensive introduction course.

  • 3 x 2-hour lessons
  • Wing and foil equipment
  • Basic wing control
  • Safety procedures
$349 Book Now

Wing Foil Mastery

Master the art of wing foiling with advanced techniques and wave riding skills.

  • 5 x 2-hour lessons
  • Advanced wing techniques
  • Wave riding instruction
  • Personalized coaching
$549 Book Now
{/* Equipment Rental */}

Equipment Rental

Kitesurfing Equipment

Rent high-quality kitesurfing gear for your sessions

  • Kites (various sizes)
  • Boards
  • Harnesses
  • Safety equipment
$50/day

Hydrofoil Equipment

Rent professional hydrofoil equipment

  • Foil boards
  • Foil wings
  • Masts and fuselages
  • Safety gear
$75/day

Wing Foil Equipment

Complete wing foiling setup for rent

  • Wings (various sizes)
  • Foil boards
  • Foil components
  • Safety equipment
$80/day
{/* Call to Action */}

Ready to Start Your Adventure?

Book your lesson today and experience the thrill of water sports with our expert instructors.

Book Your Consultation
); } export default Products;
